S.FORM: O Pakeriran (Holam: ) cacey kamoko'ay a tilifi ega i Taywan. Misanga' Pipahosoan to tilifi no Yen cu min ci ina to tilifi ega. Mipasadak to 2017 a miheca. Mianingaya a patingso Matam Hidaw Pi'arawan to lakaw
